<h2>Legal Representation for Homebuyers</h2>
<p>Buying a home or commercial property is one of the most significant financial decisions you will make. Having an experienced real estate attorney on your side ensures your interests are protected throughout the entire process.</p>
<p>At Ament Law Group, we provide legal advice and representation for buyers in preparation of agreements, due diligence, and negotiations in the purchase of residential and commercial property.</p>
<h2>How We Help Buyers</h2>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Agreement of Sale Review & Drafting</strong> — We review or prepare your purchase agreement to ensure it protects your interests and addresses important contingencies.</li>
    <li><strong>Due Diligence</strong> — We help you understand what you're buying by reviewing title history, zoning issues, easements, and other property concerns.</li>
    <li><strong>Negotiation Support</strong> — We assist with negotiations on price, repair credits, and contract terms.</li>
    <li><strong>Closing Representation</strong> — We attend the closing on your behalf to ensure all documents are accurate and your interests are protected.</li>
</ul>
<h2>Buying Without a Realtor?</h2>
<p>Buying or selling without a realtor can be a daunting task. Our attorneys can craft the Agreement of Sale to fit your needs, helping you understand the purchasing process and avoid pitfalls that can derail a transaction.</p>
